Interface IPersonalInfoUpdate

All Known Implementing Classes:
Patient
public interface IPersonalInfoUpdate
The `IPersonalInfoUpdate` interface provides a contract for objects that allow personal contact information updates, such as email and phone number. Implementing classes are expected to provide logic for updating individual contact details as well as a method to update both email and contact number together.
